 new observations regarding the discrete eigenvalues of the\ntransport operator for general dimensions and free-path distributions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 5 Dec 2013 02:29:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 6 Dec 2013 08:55:08 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 12 Jan 2014 06:09:20 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 15 Jan 2014 03:41:10 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Wed, 26 Mar 2014 01:36:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-07-02"}
