g that our algorithms are optimal as a function of the\nerror.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 5 Dec 2013 02:53:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 7 Oct 2014 20:00:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-10-09"}
